{"title":"荷叶地","authors":["忆明珠"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":5,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷叶地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆明珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地形象大半张荷叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾斜地铺在水上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水面象一环月牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将荷叶揽入了臂膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——荷叶地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地名也沁着幽香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天里桃花照水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天里绿荫蝉唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天里白鹭红蓼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天里雪压翠篁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——荷叶地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个美丽的村庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷叶上有颗露珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水晶般透明透亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露珠儿荡漾、荡漾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引多少倾慕的眼光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——荷叶地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷叶上有个姑娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聪明、俊俏、善良，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十里出众无双。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱一曲采莲的俚歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊动了记者来访。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——荷叶地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采莲歌唱到了电视上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水乡里摇桨的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用歌声迷醉了四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娇妍的荷花出水了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看样子要捧上青云乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——荷叶地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浅水怎将龙女藏？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘的心灵象露珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露珠儿在荷叶上荡漾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身影在荧光屏里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿向家乡歌唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“荷叶地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷花不离荷叶旁！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}